API Definition - Logistics Tracking System
API Information

API Name: LogisticsTrackingAPI

API Type: HTTP API

Region: ap-south-1

Stage: $default

Authorization: NONE

CORS: Disabled

Base URL
https://c4jd7eoes1.execute-api.ap-south-1.amazonaws.com
Register Package Endpoint
Endpoint
POST /register-package
Full URL
https://c4jd7eoes1.execute-api.ap-south-1.amazonaws.com/register-package
Description

Registers a package in the logistics tracking system. Package information is stored in Amazon DynamoDB for further processing.

Sample Request
{
  "packageId": "PKG1001",
  "customerName": "Rahul Sharma",
  "email": "rahul@gmail.com",
  "status": "Received"
}
Sample Success Response
Status: Succeeded
Test Event Name: der

Response:
{
  "statusCode": 200,
  "body": "\"Package PKG1001 for Rahul Sharma has arrived at Mumbai\""
}
